Task: Implement a Demo Blog Website

    Description: Create a simple blog website using Next.js. Users should be able to view a list of blog posts on the homepage and click on a post to view its details.
    Requirements:
        Use Next.js for server-side rendering and routing.
        Fetch blog post data from a mock API or a JSON file.
        Display a list of blog posts on the homepage.
        Implement a separate page to display the details of each blog post when clicked.
        Include basic styling to make the website visually appealing.
    Bonus:
        Add pagination to the homepage to handle a large number of blog posts efficiently.
        Implement search functionality to allow users to search for specific blog posts.
        Use CSS frameworks like Tailwind CSS for styling.

 1 Day
